1. *Odbili* su moju ponudu za saradnju. (They rejected my offer for cooperation.)
2. Nisam uspeo da *odbijem* tu poslasticu. (I couldn't resist that dessert.)
3. *Odbijaju* da se sastanemo sa njima. (They refuse to meet with us.)
4. Moram da *odbijem* tvoj poziv jer imam obaveze. (I have to decline your invitation because I have obligations.)
5. Advokat će *odbiti* tužbu protiv nas. (The lawyer will reject the lawsuit against us.)
6. Njen stav je da se ne sme *odbijati* pomoć drugih. (Her position is that one should not refuse help from others.)
7. Kako si *odbio* da odeš s njima na izlet? (Why did you refuse to go on a trip with them?)
8. Da bi sprečili infekciju, lekari će *odbiti* pristup bolesniku. (To prevent infection, doctors will deny access to the patient.)
9. Ne želim da te *odbacim*, ali ne mogu da prihvatim tvoje ponašanje. (I don't want to reject you, but I can't accept your behavior.)
10. Firma će *odbijati* sve neispravne proizvode. (The company will reject all defective products.)